<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/miku-maekawa" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3522164); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3522164&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200736" alt="Miku Maekawa" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3522164)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/miku-maekawa" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3522164); return false;">Miku Maekawa</a></span></p>
